# Title: Clearing Windows Console History
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-11-25
# Level: high
# Description: Identifies when a user attempts to clear console history. An adversary may clear the command history of a compromised account to conceal the actions undertaken during an intrusion.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1070, attack.t1070.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_clearing_windows_console_history.yml

ScriptBlockText="*Clear-History*" OR (ScriptBlockText IN ("*Remove-Item*", "*rm*") ScriptBlockText IN ("*ConsoleHost_history.txt*", "*(Get-PSReadlineOption).HistorySavePath*"))